Date/Jalali version 0.01
========================

Date::Jalali

   Gregorian<->Jalali Date Convetor

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 None!

